flowchart TB
    User[User / Driver Browser]

    User -->|HTTPS| CloudFront
    CloudFront --> S3[S3 React SPA]
    CloudFront -->|API Requests| ALB[Application Load Balancer]

    subgraph AWS_EKS[AWS EKS Cluster]
        ALB --> Ingress[Ingress Controller]

        subgraph Backend[Backend Services]
            Auth[Auth Service]
            UserSvc[User Service]
            DriverSvc[Driver Service]
            RideSvc[Ride Service]
            PaymentSvc[Payment Service]
        end

        Ingress --> Auth
        Ingress --> UserSvc
        Ingress --> DriverSvc
        Ingress --> RideSvc
        Ingress --> PaymentSvc
    end

    Auth --> MySQL[(MySQL)]
    UserSvc --> MySQL
    DriverSvc --> MySQL
    RideSvc --> MySQL
    PaymentSvc --> MySQL

    Auth --> Redis[(Redis)]
    RideSvc --> Redis
    DriverSvc --> Redis

    subgraph CICD[CI / CD]
        GitHub[GitHub Repository]
        GHA[GitHub Actions]
    end

    GitHub --> GHA
    GHA -->|Build & Deploy| AWS_EKS
    GHA -->|Build & Upload| S3
